:0,"updated_at":1504865590,"created_at":1504865590,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41912","user":{"id":"190196","nickname":"围观喵喵喵","avatar_url":"https://static-user-center.codemao.cn/user_0006.png","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>楼主资料搜索能力MAX</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504846623,"created_at":1504846623,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41906","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504845887,"created_at":1504845887,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41895","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>其实作业作为巩固知识的方式来说还是很有效的呢~</p>\n<p>当然啦！过重的作业负担就不该提倡了~</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504834989,"created_at":1504834989,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41853","user":{"id":"206348","nickname":"Monica老莫","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjln215RiKU5IjvGRd-KqQiJh8AL?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>真6了，不过我们老师布置的作业非常少的</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504785335,"created_at":1504785335,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41852","user":{"id":"331152","nickname":"顺铂","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMzMxMTUyXzMzMTE1Ml8xNjYyNzg3ODIzNjU5X2RhODRlZDVm.jpeg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>大力支持</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504784039,"created_at":1504784039,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41846","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>可以呀~</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504779452,"created_at":1504779452,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41838","user":{"id":"194148","nickname":"MAlopos","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTk0MTQ4XzE5NDE0OF8xNjEzMzExNDQ1ODY5XzZlYmRkN2E0.jpeg","subject_id":615,"work_shop_name":"萌新院","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我可以搬到萌新院科普库</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504778462,"created_at":1504778462,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41831","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>本文为科普喵原创，如需搬运记得署名哦~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/OK.gif\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504767314,"created_at":1504767314,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41830","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">按欧洲历史来看，最早的教育制度可以追溯到1095年的罗马帝国，只是此教育制度实行没多久，罗马帝国就陷落了，但此后的拜占庭帝国应该承袭了部分类似的制度，因此我们有理由猜测，早在1095年，作业制度就已经存在了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">但仔细思考，早在春秋战国时期，孔子就成立了第一所私塾。而私塾的前身甚至可以追溯到西周时的“<span style=\"text-align: left;\">塾</span>”。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\">根据《学记》追述西周学制所说：“古之教者，家有塾、党有庠、术有序、国有学。”</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">也就是说，其实当时就已经存在了比较完善的教育体系了。而在这种体系之下，当老师不在，而又需要学生自己温故知新的时候，“作业”的出现几乎就成了必然了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">历史上，孔子曾经分别给颜回,子路,子贡等弟子讲解关于仁的问题，并要求次日得到他们自己的看法。如此看来，这可以算是当今课后作业的前身了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img1.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2526721624,2804805984&amp;fm=214&amp;gp=0.jpg\"></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504767261,"created_at":1504767261,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41829","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">那么这个男人究竟是谁呢？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">在搜图网站上搜索了这张图片之后</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">除了臆造的类似图片，有这么一张照片吸引了我的注意力</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgspHSQdsTMOPwfi3K1pEnAyoGDZ\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">按照图片顺序来看，这位胡子绅士的名字应该是Burritt&nbsp;Haynes，而且只是个美国爱荷华州的不知名的小商人罢了</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">所以，可以确定这张图片是假的，伪造的。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">那么，作业到底是谁发明的呢？</p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504765977,"created_at":1504765977,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41828","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhKOnXQ2u45gB8nZ4sH6ONodwvlU\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">这位补充叙述的用户大概是这么质疑的：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#000000\">首先，在最早出现的图片版本中，写的是</font><font color=\"#ff0000\">科学家</font><font color=\"#000000\">证实了，意大利教师发明了作业。但是仔细想想，证实作业是谁发明的，和科学家有什么关系呢？应该是</font><font color=\"#ff0000\">历史学家</font><font color=\"#000000\">的活才对啊！</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#000000\">除了历史学家的愤怒之外，这位用户特意寻找了国外相关的资料库。发现了很有意思的一个事实，以Roberto Nevilis这个名字来看，</font>Roberto是一个非常典型的意大利名字（就好像张三这个中国名字一样常见），而Nevilis看起来却极其像一个编造的假名/姓（就好像一个人叫做王者荣耀或者姓百里一样），这个人在相关的名字查询网站上输入这个姓，发现匹配的名字只有一个人，而且这个人还是一个美国人！！！<font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">看起来，这位不知名的先生，不光可能不是作业的编造者，甚至很可能连名字都不是这个。</p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504765565,"created_at":1504765565,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"41827","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhhIwAZQ2Y_psbCDChZ_9Lrx-7M6\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">首先，很快就有一个名为Tim的人提出了质疑，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">他是这么说的：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">不可能是他！按照图内形容的，作业大概是在1905年才出现的。</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">但是早在1901年，美国加利福尼亚州就通过了废除作业的相关法案。</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">这说明至少在1901年之前，就有作业的存在了。因此1905年发明了作业的说法一定是假的。</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">看起来，这张图的真实性已经打折了不少。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">当然可能有训练师会问了，有没有可能是<font color=\"#ff0000\">记错了时间</font>而已呢？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">但是接下来有两个决定性的论点出现了......</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1504764993,"created_at":1504764993,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":17,"counted":true}